SECTION 1. The following barrios are hereby created in the City of Calbayog.

Barrio of Kilikili, consisting of the sitios of Guincatol-an, Cambahog, Somhag and Lonoy;

Barrio of Acedillo, consisting of the sitios of Bontay, Malorag, Palanas and Camatorog;

Barrio of Dagum, consisting of the sitios of Engagan, Nagboong, Labuyao and Guinkamalegan;

Barrio of Tomaleguis, consisting of the sitios of Rawis, Ba-ot, and Caglagting;

Barrio of Nijaga, consisting of the sitio of Nagboong Daco;

Barrio of Rizal, consisting of the sitios of Cawayan, Cag-abaca, Caballero and Cagboborac;

Barrio of Limarayon, consisting of the sitios of Gaway-gaway, Guintago-an, Cagsasalay and Lauong;

Barrio of Cacaransan, consisting of the sitios of Enora, Bontay, Camayze, Morabno, Elawod and Camalig;

Barrio of Malopalo, consisting of the sitios of Liguiron, Masarot, and Cagonga-an;

Barrio of San Isidro, consisting of the sitios of Nasipitan, Hitaosan and Cagbasiran;

Barrio of Bante, consisting of the sitios of Soboe, Egot, Borawosan and Tunga-a;

Barrio of Amampacang, consisting of the sitios of Burabod, Duro-ongan, or Baut and Oc. Lonoy;

Barrio of Amampacang, consisting of the sitios of Burabod, Duro-ongan, or Baut and Oc. Lonoy;

Barrio of Bantian, consisting of the sitios of Mangenoo, Masapara, Cauloyanan and Palanas;

Barrio of Salvacion, consisting of the sitios of Cagmanipes-Daco, Borobadjiang, Malobago and Onglob;

Barrio of Pena, consisting of the sitios of Cangoma-ud, Taboc, Canoctan Oc. and Cog-olango;

Barrio of Cagnipa, consisting of the sitios of Canoctan Or., Talahid, Bagacay and Culo;

Barrio of Binalew, consisting of the sitios of Ba-ay, Sulop and Pingket;

Barrio of Nabang, consisting of the sitio of Tagcarisan;

Barrio of Quezon, consisting of the sitios of.Loyang, Cabalwa, Datan, Dinanlan, Alalawig and Cambaisa;

Barrio of Cabacongan, consisting of the sitios of Lanquio, Esao and Henologan;

Barrio of Sinidman Or., consisting of the sitio of Caranas;

Barrio of Longsob, consisting of the sitios of Parasan, Cabadyangan and Longsob;

Barrio of Quirino, consisting of the sitios of Denaolan, Tabacno, Cagbayang and Talo-loan;

Barrio of Bohang, consisting of the sitios of Pagsanghang, Cagaguingay and Caransan;

Barrio of Bohang, consisting of the sitios of Pagsanghang, Cagaguingay and Caransan;

Barrio of Cagbilwang, consisting of the sitios of Cabugawan, Pungdol, Catan-agan, Capilihan and Cagbilwang Left; and

Barrio of Roxas, consisting of the sitio of Lonoy and Minaudiong.
